seeing as how everyone is swearing at people who post delta scirpt problem threads, ill take the time to explain.

.class is what the computer reads. When you make a file in java, its a .java file. The computer doesnt understand .java files, so it translates .java files into .class files, and thats what it understands and processes to make a server =)
